Package sbml2modelica.sbmlabstraction

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgebraicEquationAbstractionManager
    An AlgebraicEquationAbstractionManager provides functionalities for generation of AbstractAlgebraicEquation in an AbstractModel from the informations provided by a SBML Model.
    CompartmentAbstractionManager
    A CompartmentAbstractionManager provides functionalities for generation of AbstractCompartments, and their related AbstractSpecies, in an AbstractModel from the informations provided by a SBML Model.
    EventAbstractionManager
    An EventAbstractionManager provides functionalities for generation of AbstractEvents in an AbstractModel from the informations provided by a SBML Model.
    FunctionAbstractionManager
    A FunctionAbstractionManager provides functionalities for generation of AbstractFunctions in an AbstractModel from the informations provided by a SBML Model.
    ModelAbstractionManager
    A ModelAbstractionManager provides functionalities for the generation of an AbstractModel from a given SBML Model.
    ParameterAbstractionManager
    A ParameterAbstractionManager provides functionalities for generation of AbstractParameter in an AbstractModel from the informations provided by a SBML Model.
    ReactionAbstractionManager
    A ReactionAbstractionManager provides functionalities for generation of AbstractReactions, and their related AbstractSpeciesReferences, in an AbstractModel from the informations provided by a SBML Model.
